'''pronated'''

#{{anatomy}}: Having one’s [[hand]] [[rotated]] so that the [[palm]] faces the same direction as the interior angle of the [[elbow]].
#{{anatomy}}: Having one's [[foot]] [[twisted]] so that if walking, the weight would be borne on the inner edge of the foot.

